# OnPrem PDF API

**Self-hosted PDF rendering engine for compliance-critical systems.**

OnPrem PDF API allows you to generate high-quality PDF documents via a REST API,
running entirely on your own servers.

No cloud.  
No telemetry.  
No subscriptions.  
No external services.

---

## What is this?

OnPrem PDF API is a locally installed document rendering engine designed for
companies that must not send customer data to third-party cloud services.

It is built for:

- Insurance companies  
- Banks  
- ERP systems  
- Healthcare providers  
- Government-related systems  
- Any environment with strict data protection rules  

---

## Features

- REST API for PDF generation  
- Runs 100 % on-premise  
- No internet required after installation  
- No data storage  
- No external calls  
- Self-contained engine  
- Admin interface with license management  

