## Quick Installation

Install on any modern Linux server:

```bash
curl -fL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/onprem-pdf/api-installer/main/install.txt | sudo bash


After installation, the API is available at:

http://SERVER-IP:8080/api/v1/render

curl -X POST http://SERVER-IP:8080/api/v1/render \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "title": "Damage Report",
    "subtitle": "Date: 2026-01-10",
    "fields": [
      { "label": "Name", "value": "Max Mustermann" },
